  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening and Expanding Displacement Tracking Activities and Coordination in North East Nigeria</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Through this project, IOM seeks to strengthen and build on the data collection system already in place in the states of Adamawa, Borno and Yobe states (Nigeria) through the continuation and improvement of the Displacement Tracking Matrix (DTM) project and Biometric Registration in order to help the humanitarian community in addressing the needs of the most vulnerable affected populations.</narrative>
